1. Introduction
---------------
	This program was primarily created because my brother, Jeff, wanted
	some more realism in his basketball games. As an avid N.B.A. follower
	he wanted to see the right team names, player names, numbers, heights
	and some more realistic attributes in his own games.

	TVSBBE is a program that allows you to edit the data files for the
	Cinemaware T.V. Sports Basketball game to configure the teams and
	players to be anything you want. You can edit team names, coaches
	names, players names, players heights, players numbers and the six
	available player attributes - Shooting, Passing, Defense, Rebounding,
	Quickness and Jumping. Unlike the editor built into the T.V. Sports
	Basketball game the values of the player attributes are not
	restricted in any way.

